overview: Perky and put-together brunette Aubree Valentine has a date with a really cute guy, so that means a date-night make-up tutorial for all her fans. Aaliyah Hadid is a demure secretary working her butt off to make sure her boss gets everything he needs to get the job done. Mi Ha Doan is volunteering at a soup kitchen because she loves to give back to her community. Paige is raising money so her college choir can go to the regional championships. Bouncy blonde prep Alix Lynx is running for student council president in her crisp uniform, while also showing you her secret slutty side.
title: Look at Her Now 5
